WEBVTT

00:01:59.311 --> 00:02:02.684
and inspired waves
of social media commentary

00:02:02.708 --> 00:02:04.208
and news coverage.

00:02:05.407 --> 00:02:07.724
And I think people were surprised

00:02:07.748 --> 00:02:10.486
that a black woman
would show such compassion

00:02:10.510 --> 00:02:11.970
for a prejudiced white man,

00:02:11.994 --> 00:02:15.431
and they were surprised
that a white man would admit his bias

00:02:15.455 --> 00:02:16.988
on national television.

00:02:18.053 --> 00:02:22.149
Not long after Gary and my viral moment,

00:02:22.173 --> 00:02:23.561
we met in person.

00:02:24.299 --> 00:02:26.920
He said that he had taken my advice.

00:02:26.944 --> 00:02:31.825
He said that my words had been
like someone wiped the dust from a window